    {
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "chapterTitle": "第二章 为什么要学习古代汉语",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "26174304_4_432-497",
          "range": "432-497",
          "rangeStart": 432,
          "rangeEnd": 497,
          "markText": "为什么要学习古代汉语？首先是为了培养阅读古书的能力，以便批判地继承祖国的文化遗产；其次是因为古代汉语对现代语文修养也有一定的帮助。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1752315106,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-07-12 18:11:46",
          "chapterUid": 4,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26174304&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=432&rangeEnd=497",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632260718f6360f96c3db?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=432&rangeEnd=497"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26174304_4_432-497",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "432-497",
      "markText": "为什么要学习古代汉语？首先是为了培养阅读古书的能力，以便批判地继承祖国的文化遗产；其次是因为古代汉语对现代语文修养也有一定的帮助。",
      "totalCount": 450,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26174304&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=432&rangeEnd=497",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632260718f6360f96c3db?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=432&rangeEnd=497"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26174304_4_1143-1226",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1143-1226",
      "markText": "我们研究中国古代文化，必须剔除其糟粕，吸收其精华。但是，如果我们连书都没有读懂，也就谈不上辨别精华和糟粕了。因此，培养阅读古书的能力，是批判地继承文化遗产的先决条件。",
      "totalCount": 403,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26174304&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1143&rangeEnd=1226",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632260718f6360f96c3db?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1143&rangeEnd=1226"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26174304_5_1899-1955",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1899-1955",
      "markText": "关于古代汉语的一般知识，大致可以分为三个方面：第一是关于文字的知识，第二是关于词汇的知识，第三是关于语法的知识。",
      "totalCount": 390,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26174304&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1899&rangeEnd=1955",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632260718f6360f96c3db?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1899&rangeEnd=1955"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26174304_4_978-1039",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "978-1039",
      "markText": "当然，我们也可以靠别人读了讲给我们听，或用现代白话文写给我们看，但是到底不如自己阅读原文那样亲切有味，而且不至于以讹传讹。",
      "totalCount": 372,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26174304&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=978&rangeEnd=1039",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632260718f6360f96c3db?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=978&rangeEnd=1039"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26174304_12_923-940",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "923-940",
      "markText": "现在广东人说“走”也还是跑的意思。",
      "totalCount": 368,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26174304&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=923&rangeEnd=940",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632260718f6360f96c3db?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=923&rangeEnd=940"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26174304_3_576-597",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "576-597",
      "markText": "所谓古代汉语，实际上就是古书里所用的语言。",
      "totalCount": 247,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26174304&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=576&rangeEnd=597",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632260718f6360f96c3db?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=576&rangeEnd=597"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26174304_7_475-547",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "475-547",
      "markText": "字的最初的一种意义叫作“本义”，字的其他意义一般是由本义生出来的，叫作“引申义”。本义和字形是有关系的，懂得这个道理，有助于了解古代汉语的字义。",
      "totalCount": 231,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26174304&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=475&rangeEnd=547",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632260718f6360f96c3db?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=475&rangeEnd=547"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26174304_5_648-695",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "648-695",
      "markText": "上古汉语是文言文的源头，所以我们应该多读一些汉代以前的文章，当然中古和近代的也要占一定的比重。",
      "totalCount": 204,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26174304&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=648&rangeEnd=695",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632260718f6360f96c3db?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=648&rangeEnd=695"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26174304_10_430-523",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "430-523",
      "markText": "通是通用，假是借用（“假”就是“借”的意思）。所谓古字通假，就是两个字通用，或者这个字借用为那个字的意思。古字通假常常是两个字读音相同或相近，其中一个算是“本字”，另一个算是“假借字”。",
      "totalCount": 195,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26174304&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=430&rangeEnd=523",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632260718f6360f96c3db?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=430&rangeEnd=523"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26174304_13_1360-1409",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "1360-1409",
      "markText": "〔骑〕用作名词时旧读jì，当“骑兵”或“骑马的人”讲。如“翩翩两骑来是谁？”（白居易《卖炭翁》）。",
      "totalCount": 192,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26174304&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1360&rangeEnd=1409",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632260718f6360f96c3db?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=1360&rangeEnd=1409"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26174304_18_2679-2701",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "2679-2701",
      "markText": "第三种用法是把行为的方式或时间和行为联系起来",
      "totalCount": 192,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26174304&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=2679&rangeEnd=2701",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632260718f6360f96c3db?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=2679&rangeEnd=2701"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26174304_5_1049-1131",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1049-1131",
      "markText": "第二，是怎样读的问题。最要紧的是先把文章看懂了。不是浮光掠影地读，不是模模糊糊地懂，而是真懂。一个字也不能放过，决不能不求甚解。这样，就应该仔细看注解，勤查工具书。",
      "totalCount": 190,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26174304&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1049&rangeEnd=1131",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632260718f6360f96c3db?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1049&rangeEnd=1131"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26174304_9_429-448",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "429-448",
      "markText": "所谓异体字，是一个字有两种以上的写法。",
      "totalCount": 187,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26174304&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=429&rangeEnd=448",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632260718f6360f96c3db?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=429&rangeEnd=448"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26174304_12_513-532",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "513-532",
      "markText": "我们读古代汉语，不怕陌生的字，而怕熟字",
      "totalCount": 187,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26174304&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=513&rangeEnd=532",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632260718f6360f96c3db?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=513&rangeEnd=532"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26174304_12_1484-1527",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "1484-1527",
      "markText": "〔无虑〕古代有副词“无虑”，不是无忧无虑的意思，而是“总有”“约有”（指数量）的意思。",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26174304&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1484&rangeEnd=1527",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632260718f6360f96c3db?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1484&rangeEnd=1527"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26174304_18_8410-8448",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "8410-8448",
      "markText": "如果把现代汉语的“他死了”译成古代汉语的“其死矣”，那是不合古代汉语语法的。",
      "totalCount": 176,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26174304&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=8410&rangeEnd=8448",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632260718f6360f96c3db?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=8410&rangeEnd=8448"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26174304_7_2182-2213",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2182-2213",
      "markText": "“页”不是书页的“页”，而是音颉（xié）。“页”是头的意思。",
      "totalCount": 170,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26174304&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2182&rangeEnd=2213",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632260718f6360f96c3db?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2182&rangeEnd=2213"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26174304_5_955-1020",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "955-1020",
      "markText": "初学古代汉语不应该贪多：先不忙看《诗经选》《史记选》等，更不必全部阅读《论语》《孟子》等。“贪多嚼不烂”，这是我们应该引以为戒的。",
      "totalCount": 156,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26174304&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=955&rangeEnd=1020",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632260718f6360f96c3db?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=955&rangeEnd=1020"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26174304_8_4321-4398",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "4321-4398",
      "markText": "古代“乾”“幹”“干”不通用。“乾”是乾燥的“乾”,“幹”是树幹、躯幹的“幹”（这个意义又写作“榦”）和才幹的“幹”,“干”是盾牌（“干戈”二字常常连用）",
      "totalCount": 153,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26174304&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=4321&rangeEnd=4398",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632260718f6360f96c3db?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=4321&rangeEnd=4398"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26174304_5_1611-1640",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1611-1640",
      "markText": "学习古代汉语的人必须学会查字典，并且养成经常查字典的习惯。",
      "totalCount": 132,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26174304&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1611&rangeEnd=1640",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632260718f6360f96c3db?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1611&rangeEnd=1640"
    }
  ],
